 2023-05822023-06-16ISC
ActFirst Nations Commercial and Industrial Development Act
SubjectSquamish Nation Residential Tenancy Regulations
PrecisSQUAMISH NATION RESIDENTIAL TENANCY REGULATIONS in order to (1) incorporate by reference certain key elements from British Columbia's Residential Tenancy Act and Manufactured Home Park Tenancy Act; and (2) provide the Squamish Nation with a process to request that the Regulations be applied to future residential projects on their reserve land.
